{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"copy","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"readonly","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"title","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Although this property is optional, if you support the selection of annotations"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in your map view, you are expected to provide this property. This string is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed in the callout for the associated annotation."}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/title"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNAnnotation(py)title","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"title"}],"title":"title","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"title"}],"symbolKind":"property"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/title","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The string containing the annotation’s title."}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"]]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation/title":{"abstract":[{"text":"The string containing the annotation’s title.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/title","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/